unfavorable competition (for example in the automotive sector) against the countries and companies of the RCEP. Europe must draw the consequences of the RCEP and find customs solutions towards the north, towards Russia, and towards North Africa or achieve a real partnership with the new Asian leader under penalty of seeing ", mdx("strong", {
    parentName: "p"
